F.Cu, B.Cu, F.SilkS, B.SilkS, F.Mask, B.Mask, Edge.Cuts

- Click **Plot**

### ğŸ•³ï¸ Generate Drill Files
- Click **Generate Drill Files** after Gerber generation  

### ğŸ§¾ Check Gerbers
- Open **GerbView** or use an **online Gerber viewer** to verify  

### ğŸ“‹ Generate BOM (Bill of Materials)
- From schematic â†’ **Tools â†’ Generate BOM**  
- Include component name, value, footprint, and quantity  

